Alias           My_D0           D0
Alias           My_anti-D0      anti-D0
ChargeConj      My_D0           My_anti-D0
	
# B+->D0 BR from PDG (then renormalised to 1)
# B+ -> D0 e nu 0.02270
# B+ -> D0 pi   0.00481
# B+ -> D0 K    0.00037

Decay B+sig
1.000        My_anti-D0     e+ nu_e          PHOTOS  ISGW2;
Enddecay
CDecay B-sig

# D0 BR from PDG (then renormalised to 1)
# D0 -> pi e nu 0.0355
# D0 -> K e nu 0.0289
# D0 -> K pi   0.0388

Decay My_D0
1.000        K-        e+      nu_e           PHOTOS   ISGW2;
Enddecay
CDecay My_anti-D0
	
End
